fno: In the cash market, the Nifty 50 gained 89.25 points or 0.44% to settle at 20,192.35. The NSE's India VIX, a gauge of market's expectation of volatility over the near term, fell 3.66% to 10.90. HDFC Bank, Reliance Industries (RIL) and ICICI Bank were the top traded individual stock futures contracts in F&O segment of NSE. The September 2023 F&O contracts will expire on 28 September 2023.
